org.melior.client.web.rest

Class RestResponseExceptionMapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.melior.client.web.rest.RestResponseExceptionMapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.melior.client.exception.ResponseExceptionMapper

    public class RestResponseExceptionMapper
extends Object
implements org.melior.client.exception.ResponseExceptionMapper
    Generates a standard RemotingException from an exception payload which is received when an exception is raised in an application which processes HTTP REST requests.

    The mapper fully supports the standard exception payload that is defined by Melior, as well as the default exception payload that is defined by Spring Boot, but the mapper will function equally well with any exception payload that contains at the very least a "message" parameter.

    The mapper converts the HTTP status code of the HTTP response which contains the exception payload into an appropriate exception type for the RemotingException.

    Since:
    2.0
    Author:
    Melior
